     H            Y.
     F** CACR01 **************************
     F* .. MATERIAL COLOR JUDGMENT M/F UPDATE .. *
     F* I-HASADA            93.04.22     *
     F************************** CACR01 **
     FCACPL01 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FFCETL06 IF  E           K        DISK
     FCACPW01 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     E                    ER      1  12 60
     E                    TAB1    1   3  1   TAB2    9
     E                    #ILO    1  23  1
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80C1SKHZ
     I                                        1   40C1SKYY
     I                                        5   60C1SKMM
     I                                        7   80C1SKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80C1KOHZ
     I                                        1   40C1KOYY
     I                                        5   60C1KOMM
     I                                        7   80C1KODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60C1TIME
     I                                        1   20C1KOHH
     I                                        3   40C1KOSS
     I*           DS
     I*                                       1  10 @ZIKAN
     I*                                       2   9 @@KAN
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PUS    10
      *
     C           @ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @KAN    1
      *
     C*--------------
     C* 1 fﾞx]ﾍｭcﾆﾞ -
     C*--------------
     C           STEP2     TAG
     C                     EXFMTCACPW011
     C                     SETOF                     010203
     C                     SETOF                     99
      *
     C*-----------
     C* CMD-1 ON -
     C*-----------
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
      *
     C*-------
     C* CMD8 -
     C*-------
     C           *INKH     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KAN
     C                     CALL 'GKBR30'  @ENTRY
     C                     SETOF                     010203
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C           @KAN      IFEQ '*'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVE ER,5      MSG
     C                     END
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C*-----------
     C* ﾃcﾆ]hﾎﾞ] -
     C*-----------
     C           @CD       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,1      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @CD       IFNE '0'
     C           @CD       ANDNE'1'
     C           @CD       ANDNE'2'
     C                     MOVE ER,2      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETOF                     60
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @COD
     C           @CD       LOKUPTAB1      TAB2           60
     C           *IN60     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELTAB2      @COD
     C                     END
      *
     C*------------
     C* ﾅﾞbﾆlﾃｰnﾞ -
     C*------------
     C           @ZAICD    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,3      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETOF                     10
     C           @ZAICD    CHAINFCETL061             10
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE ER,4      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE @ZAICD    @ZICD
     C                     MOVE A2ZANM    @ZAINM
      *
     C                     SETOF                     40
     C           @ZAICD    CHAINCACPL011             40
      *
     C* nﾒiﾆ
     C* s]ﾃc
     C           @CD       IFEQ '0'
     C           @CD       OREQ '1'
     C           *IN40     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE ER,10     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010299
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
     C           C1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           C1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     MOVE ER,11     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010299
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE C1ZAIR    @ZIRCD
     C                     MOVE C1IR01    @ZIKNA
     C***                  MOVE C1IR02    @ZIKAN
     C                     END
      *
     C* lbf
     C           @CD       IFEQ '2'
     C           *IN40     IFEQ '0'
     C           C1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           C1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE ER,12     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010299
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @ZIRCD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @ZIKNA
     C***                  MOVE *BLANK    @ZIKAN
     C                     END
      *
     C*--------------
     C* 2 fﾞx]ﾍｭcﾆﾞ -
     C*--------------
     C           STEP3     TAG
     C                     EXFMTCACPW012
     C                     SETOF                     030405
     C                     SETOF                     99
      *
     C*-----------
     C* CMD-3/ON -
     C*-----------
     C           *INKC     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @CD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @ZAICD
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C*--------------
     C* ﾅﾞbﾆlbﾜﾃｰnﾞ -
     C*--------------
     C           @ZIRCD    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,6      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     GOTO STEP3
     C                     END
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         B       20
     C           @ZIRCD    LOKUP#ILO                     20
     C           *IN20     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE ER,7      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     GOTO STEP3
     C                     END
      *
     C*--------------------
     C* ﾅﾞbﾆlbﾜ（カナ） -
     C*--------------------
     C           @ZIKNA    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,8      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0499
     C                     GOTO STEP3
     C                     END
      *
     C*--------------------
     C* ﾅﾞbﾆlbﾜ（漢字） -
     C*--------------------
     C*          @@KAN     IFEQ *BLANK
     C*                    MOVE ER,9      MSG
     C*                    SETON                     0599
     C*                    GOTO STEP3
     C*                    END
      *
     C*-------------
     C* CMD-5/ OFF -
     C*-------------
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STEP3
     C                     END
      *
     C           @CD       IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       C1SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     C1SKHZ
     C                     END
      *
     C           @CD       IFEQ '1'
     C           @CD       OREQ '2'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    C1SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         C1SKHZ
     C                     MOVE @ZAICD    C1ZACD
     C                     MOVE @ZAINM    C1ZANM
     C                     MOVE @ZIRCD    C1ZAIR
     C                     MOVE @ZIKNA    C1IR01
     C***                  MOVE @ZIKAN    C1IR02
     C                     END
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     C1KOHZ
     C                     TIME           C1TIME
     C                     MOVELPUS       C1KOME
      *
     C           *IN40     IFEQ '0'
     C                     UPDATCACPL011
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITECACPL011
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE @COD      @@CD
     C                     MOVE @ZAICD    @@ZCD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @CD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @ZAICD
     C                     GOTO STEP2
      *
**  ER (ERROR MESSAGE)
E-01 INPUT UPDATE INSTRUCTION
E-02 INPUT REASOS CODE(0.1.2)
E-03 INPUT MATERIAL CODE
E-04 THERE IS NOT THE MATERIAL CODE IN PART M/F
E-05 THERE IS NOT DATA IN INQUIRY M/F
E-06 INPUT MATERIAL COLOR CODE
E-07 INPUT CODE(A-U,W,Z)
E-08 INPUT KANA NAME INTO REVERSING FIELD
E-09 INPUT KANJI NAME INTO REVERSING FIELD
E-10 THERE IS NOT IT IN M/F
E-11 IT'D DELETED ALREADY
E-12 DATA EXISTS
** REASON CODE (TAB1)
00-CANCEL
11-CHANGE
22-ADD
** MATERIAL COLOR CODE (#ILO)
A
B
C
D
E
